column8: This crate has no dependencies, no build.rs, and contains no unsafe code.
This crate has no dependencies, no build.rs, and contains no unsafe code.
Skimmed the uses of `std` to ensure that nothing untoward is happening. Code uses `forbid(unsafe_code)` and, indeed, there are no uses of `unsafe`
sourcegraph-based diff did not see the v0.21.6 tag; I retrieved a local copy of the repo and used that for diff'ing.
